</span>
</div>

                  </div>
                <div class="pl col-time">
                  <a href="https://book.douban.com/annotation/17726730/#comments">回应</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;
                  2012-04-10 14:47
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </li>
  </ul>
  

    </div>
